These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-1::.
4 different games are played: billiard, go, mah-jongg, poker
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, ice-hockey, soccer, weightlifting
1. the person playing billiard is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the far left##1
3. the person who's sport is soccer is between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the person playing go##2
4. the person playing poker is on the far left##1
5. the person playing mah-jongg is between the person playing go and the person playing billiard##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |    3     |     4      |
| Game   | poker         | go   | mah-jongg | billiard       |
| Sport      | weightlifting | cycling | soccer   | ice-hockey |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-2::.
4 different games are played: whist, poker, monopoly, chess
There are 4 different nationalities: british, colombian, dutch, turkish
1. the turkish is between the person playing monopoly and the colombian##2
2. the person playing chess is on the far right##1
3. the dutch is on the right of the british##1
4. the person playing whist is on the left of the british##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |    3    |      4      |
| Game         | poker | whist | monopoly | chess |
| Nationality   | colombian    | turkish   | british | dutch       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-3::.
There 4 different types of food: cauliflower, corn, cranberry, kale
There are 4 different favourite colors: white, ebony, light-blue, turquise
1. the person who likes light-blue is on the right of the person eating kale##1
2. the person who likes light-blue is between the person who likes ebony and the person eating corn##2
3. the person who likes ebony is on the far left##1
4. the person who likes turquise is on the left of the person eating cranberry##1
5. the person eating corn is the person who likes turquise##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |     4      |
| Food          | kale    | cauliflower | corn   | cranberry  |
| Color   | ebony | light-blue   | turquise | white |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-4::.
4 different pets are kept: cat, lizard, pony, rat
The people have 4 different jobs:  firefighter, paramedic, scientist, project-manager
1. the paramedic is the owner of the lizard##1
2. the owner of the cat is between the firefighter and the owner of the rat##2
3. the paramedic is on the far right##1
4. the owner of the cat is on the right of the scientist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1   |   2    |     3      |    4     |
| Pet     | rat   | cat    | pony       | lizard   |
| Job   | scientist | project-manager | firefighter | paramedic |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-5::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: august, december, november, april
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, dancing, magic-tricks, skydiving
1. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the far left##1
3. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the far right##1
4. the person who's birthday is in april is between the person who's hobby is card-games and the person who's hobby is dancing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1       |    2     |     3     |       4       |
| Birthday   | august        | november | april  | december |
| Hobby      | magic-tricks | dancing  | skydiving | card-games    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-6::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, d&b, pop, salsa
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, september, may, december
1. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
2. the fan of salsa is the person who's birthday is in may##1
3. the fan of salsa is on the far right##1
4. the fan of d&b is the person who's birthday is in april##1
5. the fan of pop is between the fan of classical and the fan of d&b##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |     3     |   4    |
| Music-Genre   | d&b     | pop           | classical | salsa  |
| Birthday         | april | december | september   | may |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-7::.
City: miami, marseilles, new-york, berlin
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, motorbike, roller, snowmobile
1. the person traveling to marseilles is the person driving the bus##1
2. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person traveling to miami##1
4. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
5. the person traveling to miami is between the person driving the bus and the person traveling to new-york##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| City   | berlin   | marseilles | miami | new-york      |
| Transport     | roller | bus    | motorbike  | snowmobile |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-8::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: mystery, animation, spy, western
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, motorbike, roller, snowmobile
1. the person driving the helicopter is the person watching animation movies##1
2. the person driving the motorbike is between the person watching spy movies and the person driving the roller##2
3. the person watching mystery movies is on the far left##1
4. the person driving the helicopter is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |       2       |     3      |     4      |
| Movie-Genre       | mystery | western | spy     | animation   |
| Transport   | roller   | motorbike     | snowmobile | helicopter |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-9::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  dressmaker, entrepreneur, librarian, videographer
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: western, documentary, scientific, superhero
1. the librarian is between the person watching western movies and the dressmaker##2
2. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the dressmaker##1
3. the videographer is on the right of the dressmaker##1
4. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
5. the dressmaker is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |     3      |      4       |
| Job         | entrepreneur | librarian | dressmaker | videographer |
| Movie-Genre   | western         | superhero       | documentary    | scientific         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-10::.
City: edinburgh, hamburg, prague, hannover
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, ice-hockey, swimming, tennis
1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the person traveling to hannover##1
2. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person traveling to prague##1
3. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1
4. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
5. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is between the person traveling to hamburg and the person who's sport is tennis##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |    3     |    4     |
| City    | hannover   | prague      | hamburg   | edinburgh  |
| Sport   | tennis | ice-hockey | swimming | baseball |

