.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-11::.
4 different pets are kept: turtle, goat, frog, fish
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, fantasy, superhero, time-travel
1. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person watching fantasy movies##1
2. the owner of the goat is between the owner of the fish and the owner of the turtle##2
3. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1
4. the person watching superhero movies is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3    |      4      |
| Pet          | turtle     | goat | fish   | frog        |
| Movie-Genre   | animation | superhero   | fantasy | time-travel |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-12::.
City: miami, hamburg, venice, rome
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: gospel, pop, punk, trance
1. the fan of punk is the person traveling to hamburg##1
2. the fan of pop is on the left of the fan of trance##1
3. the fan of gospel is the person traveling to miami##1
4. the person traveling to venice is the fan of pop##1
5. the fan of gospel is on the right of the person traveling to rome##1
6. the fan of pop is between the person traveling to hamburg and the person traveling to rome##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |    3    |     4      |
| City         | hamburg | venice | rome | miami |
| Music-Genre   | punk          | pop     | trance  | gospel     |

