4. the designer is on the left of the owner of the frog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2        |    3     |     4     |
| Job           | designer | police-officer | musician | nurse     |
| Pet   | hedgehog   | frog    | chinchilla   | bird |

