.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-14::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  doctor, entrepreneur, firefighter, librarian
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, march, october, december
1. the entrepreneur is the person who's birthday is in october##1
2. the person who's birthday is in february is between the person who's birthday is in december and the person who's birthday is in march##2
3. the librarian is on the right of the doctor##1
4. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the librarian##1
5. the person who's birthday is in october is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |      3      |      4       |
| Job           | doctor | librarian | firefighter | entrepreneur |
| Birthday   | march   | february | december         | october |

