.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-19::.
There are 4 different nationalities: american, australian, chinese, polish
House: gothic-revival, farmhouse, colonial, futuristic
1. the farmhouse house is on the left of the futuristic house##1
2. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the farmhouse house##1
3. the polish is the gothic-revival house##1
4. the futuristic house is between the american and the chinese##2
5. the chinese is the colonial house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Nationality   | polish   | american   | australian | chinese |
| House         | gothic-revival | farmhouse | futuristic     | colonial    |

